<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.12">
<l>accam tiṉaittaṉai yillaiyip piḷḷaik kāṇmaiyum cēva kamum</l>
<l>ucciyil mutti vaḷartteṭut tēṉuk kuraittilaṉ tāṉiṉ ṟupōy</l>
<l>paccilaip pūṅkaṭam pēṟi vicaikoṇṭu pāyntupuk kāyi ravāy</l>
<l>naccaḻal poykaiyil nākatti ṉōṭu piṇaṅkinī vantāy pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This child does not have [even] a trifling amount of fear,</l>
<l rend="indent">only daring and heroics.</l>
<l>He does not tell me anything – me, who nurtured him nuzzling his head.</l>
<l>Having gone [out] today, climbing up a flowering, evergreen kaṭampu,</l>
<l>Leaping hastily into a pond where poison from a thousand mouths burns,</l>
<l rend="indent">it seems you came and tangled with a serpent.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
